@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy - GrowTrack";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="card-header text-white p-4 border-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #304251 0%, #4a6278 100%);">
                    <h1 class="h2 mb-0" style="color: #F3993E;">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-lg-5">
                    <div class="alert d-flex align-items-center mb-4" style="background-color: rgba(48, 66, 81, 0.1); border-color: #304251;">
                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle fs-4 me-3" style="color: #304251;"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> May 15, 2025. At GrowTrack, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your business data.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p>Welcome to GrowTrack's Privacy Policy. This document explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your business information when you use our analytics-driven CRM system. We understand the sensitivity of your business data and are committed to maintaining its confidentiality. Please read this privacy policy carefully. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not access the application.</p>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">2. Business Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>To provide meaningful business insights, GrowTrack collects information that you provide directly to us when you:</p>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3 border-0">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-light"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Register for an account</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Fill in forms within the application</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-light"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Upload documents or other content</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Communicate with us</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-light"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Participate in surveys or promotions</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">3. How We Use Your Business Data</h2>
                    <p>GrowTrack processes your business information to generate valuable insights. We may use the data we collect for various purposes, including to:</p>
                    <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 bg-light">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Generate Business Insights</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Process your business data to create actionable analytics, performance metrics, and growth forecasts.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 bg-light">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Enhance Analytics</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Continuously refine our algorithms and analytics models to provide more accurate business insights and forecasts.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 bg-light">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-envelope" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Insight Delivery</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Send you business insights, performance reports, growth opportunities, and important notifications about your account.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 bg-light">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Data Protection</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Implement robust security measures to protect your sensitive business data and prevent unauthorized access.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">4. Business Data Security</h2>
                    <p>At GrowTrack, we understand the sensitivity of your business data. We have implemented enterprise-grade security measures designed to protect your information, including encryption, access controls, and regular security audits. Our analytics platform is built with privacy by design principles. However, despite our comprehensive safeguards, no electronic transmission over the Internet or information storage technology can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.</p>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">5. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>
                    <div class="accordion mb-4" id="privacyAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                    <i class="fas fa-eye" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Right to Access
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    You have the right to request copies of your personal data. We may charge you a small fee for this service.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                    <i class="fas fa-edit" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Right to Rectification
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    You have the right to request that we correct any information you believe is inaccurate or complete information you believe is incomplete.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                    <i class="fas fa-trash-alt" style="color: #304251;" me-2"></i> Right to Erasure
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    You have the right to request that we erase your personal data, under certain conditions.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy.</p>
                    
                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">7. Contact GrowTrack Support</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your business data, please contact our dedicated support team:</p>
                    <div class="row g-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center p-3 bg-light rounded">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope fs-4" style="color: #304251;" me-3"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Email</h6>
                                    <p class="mb-0">grow.track.06@gmail.com</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center p-3 bg-light rounded">
                                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt fs-4" style="color: #304251;" me-3"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Phone</h6>
                                    <p class="mb-0">+639564186361</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
